{"quotes": [{"lines": [{"text": "Colonel, I'm gonna blow up this road. Now, how can we keep the people off?", "character": "Major Baldwin", "characterId": "nm0000071"}, {"text": "Off?", "character": "Col. Kwan", "characterId": "nm0798826"}, {"text": "Well, I-I, I need them stopped for about ten minutes. Can you do it?", "character": "Major Baldwin", "characterId": "nm0000071"}, {"text": "How?", "character": "Col. Kwan", "characterId": "nm0798826"}, {"text": "Well, uh, how 'bout, uh, how 'bout if we get a couple of empty gasoline drums, put 'em on either side of the road, stretch a rope across.", "character": "Major Baldwin", "characterId": "nm0000071"}, {"text": "They'd go under the rope.", "character": "Col. Kwan", "characterId": "nm0798826"}, {"text": "Well, then we get some Chinese soldiers to explain to them, explain to them that we're cutting the road. How 'bout that?", "character": "Major Baldwin", "characterId": "nm0000071"}, {"text": "The soldiers will want to get through themselves.", "character": "Col. Kwan", "characterId": "nm0798826"}, {"text": "Well, could we give them something?", "character": "Major Baldwin", "characterId": "nm0000071"}, {"text": "What?", "character": "Col. Kwan", "characterId": "nm0798826"}, {"text": "Well, money?", "character": "Major Baldwin", "characterId": "nm0000071"}, {"text": "They cannot spend money here.", "character": "Col. Kwan", "characterId": "nm0798826"}, {"text": "Well, food. How 'bout food? We got 'K' rations, cigarettes. How about cigarettes? What'll they take for the job?", "character": "Major Baldwin", "characterId": "nm0000071"}, {"text": "[Kwan Says something in Chinese]", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "[Angrily]\nI don't speak Chinese, Colonel.", "character": "Major Baldwin", "characterId": "nm0000071"}, {"text": "There is no way.", "character": "Col. Kwan", "characterId": "nm0798826"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "[the road gets blocked]", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "How 'bout it?", "character": "Major Baldwin", "characterId": "nm0000071"}, {"text": "The boots convinced them.", "character": "Col. Kwan", "characterId": "nm0798826"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "[last lines]", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "To the end of the road, peace and safety.", "character": "Madame Sue-Mei Hung", "characterId": "nm0523734"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "Fire in the hole! Fire in the hole!", "character": "Sgt. Michaelson", "characterId": "nm0604702"}]}]}